{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-400-fibonacci-tree-game","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 400: Igra Fibonaccijevog drveta","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Fibonacci stablo je binarno stablo definisano rekurzivno kao što sledi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$T(0)$ je prazno stablo.</li>\n<li>$T(1)$ je binarno stablo sa samo jednim čvorom.</li>\n<li>$T(k)$ sadrži korenovi čvor koji ima $T(k - 1)$ i $T(k - 2)$ kao svoje potomke.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>U drvetu poput ovog, dva igrača igra igru oduzimanja. Na svom potezu, igrač bira čvor i uklanja ga zajedno sa poddrvetom koje je taj čvor uspostavio. Igrač koji je primoran da uzme koren celog drveta gubi.</p>\n<p>Ovde su pobedeći potezi prvog igrača u prvom potezu za $T(k)$ od $k = 1$ do $k = 6$.</p>\n<img alt=\"winning moves of first player, on the first turn for k = 1 to k = 6\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/fibonacci-tree-game.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka $f(k)$ bude broj pobedničkih poteza prvog igrača (tj., potezi koje drugi igrač nema strategiju da osvoji) u prvom koraku igre kada se ova igra igra na $T(k)$.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $f(5) = 1$ i $f(10) = 17$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $f(10000)$. Navedi poslednjih 18 cifara vašeg odgovora.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4fe1000cf542c510010","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302067,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-400-fibonacci-tree-game"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function fibonacciTreeGame() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nfibonacciTreeGame();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>fibonacciTreeGame()</code> treba da vrati <code>438505383468410600</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(fibonacciTreeGame(), 438505383468410600);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-400-fibonacci-tree-game","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":true,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-401-sum-of-squares-of-divisors","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-399-squarefree-fibonacci-numbers","id":"5900f4fe1000cf542c510010","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-400-fibonacci-tree-game"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}